lead_paragraph: LOURO--Vicki Lynn, 55, of Wall Twp., NJ, died January 9, 2013. Survived by husband, Dr. Joseph Louro; sons Joseph (Cynthia) and James (Jennifer); sister, Connie Slocum; grandchildren Joseph, Juliana and Sophia. Member of NY Athletic Club and Trump National Golf Club, Colts Neck, NJ. Memorial service at St. Robert Bellarmine Church, Freehold, NJ, Saturday, January 19, 2013 at 1:00pm. Services Freeman Funeral Home, Freehold.
